  "text": "The segmentation methods are not always very specific; it is typical to have segments that clearly do not represent the objects of interest, and these have to be removed from the detections. This is a classification task (also called pattern recognition) where the classification method can range from simple object area-based rejection to deep neural networks, representing the state of the art in machine learning [CITATION_1] .",
